head.title: Meetup RSVPs v2

item.comments: So sorry for the last minute cancellation, but I just found out I have out of town visitors.

I have to cancel as the Boston Singles Golf has let me in, and it looks like a great golf day. I would have loved to walk and talk with the people in this group! See you next time, or message me and we can walk on the Charles (Waltham) Fresh Pond.
Wish I could join you, but I have to work.
